init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "What is that sparkling stuff on your popcorn?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You can sprinkle it on anything and make it better.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He smiles and hands you the whole bucket.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You suddenly feel like you can do anything: talk to anyone, learn anything, love anyone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You do this, and suddenly you are no longer sitting in a cinema.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are sitting on an unfamiliar beach, but it looks like the beach from your dreams.
